description: This skill is a twist on The Most Interesting Man in the World quotes.  You tell Alexa a name and it will insert that name within the quote.  Fun at parties!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, tell me an interesting quote about Bill from Interesting Man
Alexa, get us a manly fact about James from Interesting Man
Alexa, tell everyone a fun fact about Darren from Interesting Man
name: Interesting Man
shortDescription: Most Interesting Man quotes about anyone.
